casebody.data:
Nagel, Appellee, v. Huntington National Bank, Appellant.

[Cite as Nagel v. Huntington Natl. Bank, 122 Ohio St.3d 1227, 2009-0hio-3451.]

(No. 2008-2501 Submitted July 14, 2009 Decided July 21, 2009.) Dworken & Bernstein Co., L.P.A., and Patrick J. Perotti; and Brian G. Ruschel, for appellee. Porter, Wright, Morris & Arthur, L.L.P., Jennifer T. Mills, and L. Bradfield Hughes, for appellant.

{¶ 1} The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently accepted.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
